OOC:Well I am leavin this RPG; Goodbye and goodbye.


Sniper / Proto / Rhinox / Grimmler / Oinker / Zergling / Scorponok / 
Lobstruck / BH / BlastRage


Sniper sits in his cell, "Can I get a trial? Hello. Can I." Sniper 
waits, "Slag, I guess I don't." Sniper reached under his bunk and 
pulled out the rifle he had grabbed earlier. Sniper said on his com, 
"To all living things Death must come." Sniper fires his Rifle into 
his head killing him.

Scopronok is mad, "Darkmouse his love is not with him anymore. He
goes 
to where the original predacon base was and sends a com to Megatron, 
"Megatron, I will be taking a short leave." Scopronok dives into the 
lava.
